verbose_text: To knock down Dube3a in larval muscle we used c179-GAL4 (which expresses in embryonic mesoderm, larval muscles and wing imaginal discs, n = 9); 24B-GAL4 (also known as how 24B -GAL4 which expresses in both embryonic and larval somatic muscle, n = 11); and mef2-GAL4 (which expresses in somatic muscle and imaginal wing disks, n = 11).
